    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rotate, resize, and repack fantasy items in this inventory-management puzzle game.</strong><br>Scale Mail is a casual game where you organize swords, gems, and... tennis balls? Using draconic magic, shrink or grow items to fit them all inside a bag while keeping it light enough to carry.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296300/extras/4c14e6b99e6660718844917a50c0a673.poster.avif?t=1770497402\" width=400 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296300/extras/4c14e6b99e6660718844917a50c0a673.webm?t=1770497402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296300/extras/4c14e6b99e6660718844917a50c0a673.mp4?t=1770497402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Charming Art</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pack 50+ unique, hand-drawn items across 18 levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296300/extras/8f488d680a7ad0e44b4ada8b9ef29cc1.avif?t=1770497402\" width=300 height=233 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Peculiar Patrons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet mysterious and charming clients, each with uniquely-shaped bags and quirky sets of items to pack in them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296300/extras/ad2605e8ac39f27c6b94b711f2bf1006.avif?t=1770497402\" width=200 height=199 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296300/extras/53918909f11a9a17f7de4963613cfc4f.avif?t=1770497402\" width=200 height=200 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296300/extras/f1df5a3a9bd2aead55a42a48102d3aea.avif?t=1770497402\" width=200 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Grow your Hoard</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill any extra shipping space with sweets to earn stars, each one contributing to your hoard of gold!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296300/extras/32e3f508a2be9d9220b194d26d3573db.avif?t=1770497402\" width=600 height=456 /></span></p>",
